data.description: BASEMENT RANCH in Blount County! Close to town and the Great Smoky Mountains. This three bedroom/two bathroom home has been updated throughout. New waterproof lvp flooring, no carpet. Both bathrooms have been updated. The home has brand new windows with a transferable warranty, and a newly remodeled basement with a 125'' projector screen. The kitchen offers new appliances, countertops, and a new backsplash. This home boasts a lovely open concept and a large open basement rec room. There is plumbing under the floor in the basement to add a third bathroom if desired. Call today to schedule your private showing.
